{"tid":1571781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【916】再唔腥email就得番操你媽傻逼！","createTime":"2019-09-15T13:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:34:26.000Z","uid":92277,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9692de0bba39a65b00c0962b651ea400a64eee","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"*我抄隔黎post既，因為太重要！<br />\n<br />\n中文科取消聆聽,說話嘅諮詢文件。應該係想幫內地生爭學位, 同埋淡化甚至消滅廣東話!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=12fa9fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔同意，請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、<br />\n電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔<br />\n皇后大道東 213 號<br />\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」<br />\n<br />\n_________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Template在此👇，標題請自行撰寫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n致專責小組成員：<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港市民，有聞 貴組於6月28日文件中提出刪去文憑試聆聽及說話考卷，本人堅表強烈反對，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n一，掌握母語不等於能以母語表達，說話要言之有物、出口成文，除了要豐富的詞彙，亦要有清晰的表達方式，說話卷的核心價值在於檢視學生在日常用語之外，能否有效建構論點展開討論，而廢除後則無地方訓練學生這頂基本能力。<br />\n<br />\n二，掌握母語不等於能理解別人話語內容，聆聽別人的說話可以訓練學生將對話精煉的能力，亦即是捕捉重點的能力，假如廢除，恐怕學生會失去一個練習的平台，無法與人有效溝通。<br />\n<br />\n三，以語言系公開試ielts雅思為例，考核學生英語水平以讀聽寫說四考卷，尤其是以說話難度最高，一向是該考試衡量英語高水平者的好標準，如今 貴組研廢除聆、說二卷，猶如自斷一臂。<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上及眾多學者之言，冀 貴組於此項教育改革方向予於重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpGhiqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpGhiqO.jpg&h=f493d0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">腥完share埋比fd, 再留言話Done! </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShared From fb"},{"pid":"709acda0a983cacbdb696bd228c9ced2a6ac24b9","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">操你媽逼電郵都不敢發喔？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ddf078f689ee6f3e91f1965ada907d285a84551c","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"一堆傻逼還說鍵盤戰士？"},{"pid":"e8bab1779bd4ff31d60f33c6a2ca0bdeb9ce14b0","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"有種發個電郵來呀幹你娘傻逼"},{"pid":"dd5897849eaf79444d23026f83acfb7852ded0c2","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:55:59.000Z","msg":"操 一個能打的都沒有"},{"pid":"113408f80f5ec2bb2e6eb3400c5b0741c166a344","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"人人都說抗爭<br />\n結果呢？真香"},{"pid":"d9dda9f57e4a80c751279b204920c65668d28dec","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"操你媽救人啦"},{"pid":"6a73ae29efa978b413f314306f8d26487fa2b88a","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"屌你地"},{"pid":"f23bcbe1d678dabfb7032d20d4ef5f35a1e9b041","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"教育好撚重要呀知唔知呀"},{"pid":"927f5194c03b27845891d3936b8d2e20a2197116","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"腥封email都懶"},{"pid":"486716ef351146581ac76accc7e1db6ab944d6bf","tid":1571781,"uid":51368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"cfbe78d1604bbacb794a9cf2ad7d4af5a818c4fe","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c