le=\"color: red;\">最新版本會長駐個post最底部</span><br />\n黑警罪證 避免阻止大家睇post 以後會用貼link方式推post 請大家有時間㩒入嚟睇一睇 用心記住黑警嘅惡行 手足所受嘅傷<br />\n無論如何都絕不可以原諒黑警 要佢哋血債血償 將呢3個月香港人所受嘅苦全部償還 <br />\n一個人力量太小 如果有遺留 可以自己更新/同我講 亦請有識之士幫手翻譯不同版本<br />\n感激大家 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n黑警罪證 15/9更新版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f7d00648ce434c0dc6801a78d41559ea7626340","tid":1571781,"uid":100356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"186b9c61dcf9e4db9e4f78d57c7db4f837138584","tid":1571781,"uid":236777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"希望大家瘋狂宣傳黑警執法不公呢樣野！！！<br />\n唔好畀手足既血白流！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhgQD7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhgQD7b.jpg&h=8f0fcabe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ec5d9cc1424ae3a4205902534f43ff765a5fd0e","tid":1571781,"uid":294797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9692de0bba39a65b00c0962b651ea400a64eee","tid":1571781,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"*我抄隔黎post既，因為太重要！<br />\n<br />\n中文科取消聆聽,說話嘅諮詢文件。應該係想幫內地生爭學位, 同埋淡化甚至消滅廣東話!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=12fa9fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔同意，請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、<br />\n電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔<br />\n皇后大道東 213 號<br />\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」<br />\n<br />\n_________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Template在此👇，標題請自行撰寫</span></span><br />\n<br 